n the original source, which changes the meaning of what needs to be positioned above this handler.\n\nI'm also realizing I need to be more systematic about checking for PascalCase class names. FwHeaderReader appears in the s1 content but isn't captured in the s1 hints—that's a concrete finding. Let me continue scanning for other class names I might have missed, like ServiceAvailability which I can confirm is already properly included in s3.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":18718,"cache_read_input_tokens":29807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":18718,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"71a0e496-e9a4-4daa-91a4-9381bc4df157","uuid":"4fe907d1-4eee-48b5-b300-172a797eea01"}
